PRIVACY
Privacy Statement
This Privacy Statement explains our practices regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of certain information, including your personal information, by the Eye Of The Tiger Tech, Inc. ("Eye Of The Tiger").
​
Contacting Us
If you have general questions about your account or would like to contact Customer Service for assistance, please visit
https://eyeofthetigertech.com/contact
. For questions specifically about this Privacy Statement, or our use of your personal information, cookies or similar technologies, please contact us by email at
support@eyeofthetigertech.com
.
​
Collection of Information
Eye Of The Tiger is committed to ensuring your private and personal information is protected. We do not share your information with any third parties and we encrypt all of your private and personal information.
